eplyTime":"2019-09-25T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"幫推呀"},{"pid":"921d083d750dec90f265129fc1aab112b906eee7","tid":1587823,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5bcbf94b26247445d08020f8c9b77b0b38db534","tid":1587823,"uid":84882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"可唔可以先扮客觀咁過左接聽生果過，在係節目到勁黃"},{"pid":"48ecfaccec30a50fa9c6baa971a5bcf43309ef52","tid":1587823,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c892ce7a9c353c8ea34640e8e2b410157d57b785","tid":1587823,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a5da857f18bc5f5aae2c367b1fbf77af3a8f672","tid":1587823,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6775c15004490852a44a1d4b3c0fcf2986802c64","tid":1587823,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19688bb8f046e9dfe210146f1b4fb4307b1bcbf4","tid":1587823,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8f9911e947bad624cc8de4616935b2f3734a1b","tid":1587823,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46061dd9a4f3734882209220255b5d745ef50b6f","tid":1587823,"uid":321684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都要推"},{"pid":"e51664b3f3f06c057ceb64b39dd06228fe86455c","tid":1587823,"uid":40028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80fcff580dbadf8a560314f46ea1c2e1a89a27d1","tid":1587823,"uid":29376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<br />\n利申：港台員工 會幫手聽電話畀人拎嚟做出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 之前都有巴打提過，港台商台逢一至五嘅phone-in節目係輿論戰場，<br />\n港台有：<br />\n08:00-10:00 香港電台第一台 千禧年代 / Phone-in tel no. : 1872311<br />\n170:0-18:00, 19:00-20:00 香港電台第一台 自由風自由Phone / Phone-in tel no. : 1872311<br />\n商台有：<br />\n06:30-07:00, 07:15-10:00 雷霆881 (陳志雲版) 08:00-10:00 叱咤903 (潘小濤版)<br />\n在晴朗的一天出發 / Phone-in 電話: 1872881 (陳) / 1872903 (潘)<br />\n<br />\n咁我唔知隔離台做法係咪一樣，但我可以話你知，呢啲節目長期有人打緊入嚟，<br />\n我哋一節會接成百個call,但時間所限，其實每日只係出到3-6個。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有打過入嚟都知，接線生會要你留電話號碼、姓氏同埋想講嘅題目，<br />\n我哋聽電話嘅要成個人肉錄音機咁，因為老細可能聽住，我哋講太有引導性嘅話，<br />\n係可能畀聽眾錄音搞鳩或者收投訴，咁老細係好緊張的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以只會不斷重複「幫你登記」「盡量安排」等，你咩都唔留又唔講想講咩，我哋只會話「先生同你傾到呢度」<br />\n但phone-in個玩法到底係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋係絕對會做過濾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有好多打上嚟嘅都係廢老都係鳩噏鳩屌，言之無物，<br />\n而大氣電波係好寶貴嘅資源，我哋係冇可能駁個痴線嘅入去，<br />\n咁樣係會令主持人難做同埋無阻推進成個討論。<br />\n但係，如果你只係話想講XXX呢個話題e.g.警察濫捕，我哋一樣係唔鳩會理你，因為判斷唔到你想講咩。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁我哋想要咩嘅聽眾？</span></span><br />\n作為一個懶中肯又對到廢老口味嘅phone-in節目，我哋成日要邀請兩邊嘅聲音，<br />\n黃同藍都會考慮，所以唔會以政見為由去過濾聽眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過時間真係好tight，一針見血、一語中的嘅說話係最好。<br />\n我哋係要啲講得好嘅聽眾，所以你打到入嚟，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實係先要說服到接線生，<br />\n你係有條理、有理有據嘅正常人</span>（bonus係你有好親身嘅經驗/用詞好精準聽落好好聽，<br />\n但唔好太假，例如你話自己係831太子站目擊證人呢啲係冇人會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n然後接線生就會過畀節目編導睇，由編導決定呢個人出唔出得街。<br />\n其實你可以當同接線生傾時係一次練習，組織一段好聽嘅speech，<br />\n到入到直播室同主持傾時，講返一樣嘅嘢就得，咁就唔驚1999啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅你哋有好多嘢幫到勇武㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphone-in節目係你哋嘅主場，好好用嚟帶風，唔好畀啲傻閪廢老有機可乘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4495281a4873649e454dc5ca050d6982698a111","tid":1587823,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:50:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b5b2fc9353bcf92c2fd19540c17d9d6ea8b6dfc7","tid":1587823,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:52:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0a42816c34608a47ad2f3d5920005718283ddf5","tid":1587823,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:00:39.000Z","msg":"讚"},{"pid":"6ccd57d0a91c180420c881e02c133f1bcc295960","tid":1587823,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:23:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9888aeb92c89ea7aa3d4d668125364881d222681","tid":1587823,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31d15a165286bce5503331a85fcf926e4a43b7bd","tid":1587823,"uid":269001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"推 我日日聽自由風自由phone<br />\n好多基層一邊做嘢一邊聽<br />\n真係好影響到輿論"},{"pid":"3c2491d3965961454710ac5d3d3a63f8eac0be5c","tid":1587823,"uid":103326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d5a2b8d38a7faa4200db92c33c5e407a05bfb806","tid":1587823,"uid":249722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T20:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb73984ecef10b899ef0d1f8b919384804e18028","tid":1587823,"uid":261584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c